(
        //Define schema of table
        UserId          int,

        Region          string,

CREATE FUNCTION testdb14085.dbo.testtvf16439()
RETURNS @result TABLE
(
    s_date DateTime,
    s_time string,
    s_sitename string,
    cs_method string, 
    cs_uristem string,
    cs_uriquery string,

    sc_status int,
    sc_substatus int,
    sc_win32status int, 
    sc_bytes int,
    cs_bytes int,
    s_timetaken int
)
AS
BEGIN

    @result = EXTRACT
        s_date DateTime,
        s_time string,
        s_sitename string,
        cs_method string,
        cs_uristem string,
        cs_uriquery string,
        s_port int,

        cs_useragent string,
        cs_cookie string,

        cs_host string,
        sc_status int,

        sc_bytes int,

        s_timetaken int
    FROM @"/Samples/Data/WebLog.log"
    USING Extractors.Text(delimiter:' ');

RETURN;
END;
